OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1772733966
OL,3,CMemorial flights to mark 90 years
OL,4,Csince first spitfire flight
OL,6,FThe company SPITFIRES.COM is painting
OL,7,Fone of its two seat Spitfires to
OL,8,Freplicate how the K5054 looked.
OL,10,FWorking alongside the Royal Air Force,
OL,11,Fthe aircraft will then embark on a
OL,12,Ftour of the UK.
OL,14,FThe plan is for it to take off from
OL,15,FSouthampton International Airport
OL,16,F(formerly Eastleigh Airport), which
OL,17,Fwas the location of the first flight
OL,18,Fof the Spitfire.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
