OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1772733966
OL,3,CMemorial flights to mark 90 years
OL,4,Csince first spitfire flight
OL,6,FThe aircraft will circumnavigate the
OL,7,FUK overflying key Spitfire locations
OL,8,Fand landing at airports with historic
OL,9,For existing connections to the
OL,10,Faircraft.
OL,12,FDan Townsend, Head of Airside
OL,13,FOperations at Southampton Airport,
OL,14,Fsaid: "The rich history of aviation at
OL,15,FSouthampton is plain to see...History
OL,16,Fthat is through the blood of the
OL,17,Fpeople of Eastleigh and we're very
OL,18,Fproud."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
