PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1772733966
OL,3,CMemorial flights to mark 90 years
OL,4,Csince first spitfire flight
OL,6,FNine individual flights will take
OL,7,Fplace to symbolise the 90 years being
OL,8,Fcommemorated, with the Royal Air Force
OL,9,Fproviding assets to escort the
OL,10,FSpitfire at key stages during the
OL,11,Froute and showcasing their existing
OL,12,Ffleet of aircraft against the backdrop
OL,13,Fof this anniversary of their most
OL,14,Ffamous fighter.
OL,16,FThe first light will begin on Tuesday
OL,17,F7th April, with one flight taking
OL,18,Fplace per day (excluding weekends),
OL,19,Fand concluding on Friday 17th April.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
