PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1772733966
OL,3,CMemorial flights to mark 90 years
OL,4,Csince first spitfire flight
OL,6,FA new Spitfire wall, reaching 12
OL,7,Fmetres long, is planned to be created
OL,8,Fto celebrate the Spitfire's first
OL,9,Fflight and its creator R.J Mitchell,
OL,10,Falongisde its Test Pilot Joseph "Mutt"
OL,11,FSummers.
OL,13,FThe new artwork frames the two unique
OL,14,Fplaques and offers a rich photo
OL,15,Fmontage backdrop, as well as plaques
OL,16,Fand National Spitfire Memorial wind
OL,17,Ftunnel model.
